Aaron Hernandez was found guilty Wednesday of murdering Odin Lloyd in 2013 . 
  The jury that convicted him sat down for a group interview on Thursday with CNN's Anderson Cooper . 
  The seven women and five men say they believe they gave him a fair trial . 
  Most of the jurors said they knew nothing about the former New England Patriots star before the trial . 
  They say they locked eyes with Hernandez as the verdict was read on Wednesday . 
  Hernandez was sentenced to life in prison without parole . 
 